WEBVTT

00:00:01.679 --> 00:00:10.599
At Matthew 13, verse 52, Jesus said that every public instructor was like a man with a treasure

00:00:10.599 --> 00:00:15.640
store filled with truths, old and new.

00:00:15.640 --> 00:00:22.719
Well, we know that's true, and if it's true, it means that this audience are among the

00:00:22.719 --> 00:00:26.640
most rich people in the entire world.

00:00:26.640 --> 00:00:34.600
You have a large treasure store of truths, both old and new.

00:00:34.600 --> 00:00:41.880
But here's the question, what will you do with your treasure store?

00:00:41.880 --> 00:00:53.100
Now a Deuteronomy, chapter 29, and verse 29, Moses gave these words, he said,

00:00:53.100 --> 00:01:04.219
the things concealed belong to Jehovah our God, but the things revealed belong to us and

00:01:04.219 --> 00:01:12.939
to our descendants forever so that we may carry out all the words of this law.

00:01:12.939 --> 00:01:15.420
Well, there's a fundamental truth there.

00:01:15.420 --> 00:01:22.900
