00:01:22.900 --> 00:01:29.019
descendants to all of our sons and daughters who are to come.

00:01:29.019 --> 00:01:38.019
Well, that means that as men and women of faith, we have a clear responsibility to share,

00:01:38.019 --> 00:01:43.859
to pass on the wonderful truths that we have come to know with the next generation.

00:01:43.859 --> 00:01:46.859
Well, the Bible emphasizes this.

00:01:46.859 --> 00:01:58.450
Let's read that what the Psalmist said in Psalm 78 and verse 3, Psalm 78, verse 3,

00:01:58.450 --> 00:02:05.569
