So Jehovah took the matter of passing this on to the next generation very seriously because

00:02:50.169 --> 00:02:58.250
look at what it says in verse 5, it says he established a reminder in Jacob and set a

00:02:58.250 --> 00:03:00.409
law in Israel.

00:03:00.409 --> 00:03:07.250
He commanded our forefathers to make these things known to their children so that the next

00:03:07.250 --> 00:03:12.530
generation, the children yet to be born might know them.

00:03:12.530 --> 00:03:16.729
They in turn would relate them to their children.

00:03:16.729 --> 00:03:24.250
Well, brothers and sisters, especially those of you who have so much wisdom and experience,

00:03:24.250 --> 00:03:31.930
do you feel that responsibility to share what you have with the generation to come?

00:03:32.409 --> 00:03:40.409
Well, if we get the sense of Deuteronomy 29, 29 and Psalm 78, well then we will do this.

00:03:40.409 --> 00:03:46.770
We will share what we have with the next generation, but how do we do it?

00:03:46.770 --> 00:03:51.169
Well, of course, this process begins with all of our parents.

00:03:51.169 --> 00:03:58.770
And by their following, the command in Deuteronomy 6, verses 6 and 7, to teach their children as

00:03:58.849 --> 00:04:06.969
