00:04:11.650 --> 00:04:21.970
We also have a responsibility to teach and train young adults so that they can take on responsibility

00:04:21.970 --> 00:04:24.610
in Jehovah's congregation.

00:04:24.610 --> 00:04:30.649
Now the Bible is filled with examples of individuals who are wonderful trainers.

00:04:30.649 --> 00:04:34.569
Maybe one who comes to mind right away is Moses.

00:04:34.569 --> 00:04:38.689
