00:07:03.339 --> 00:07:09.420
But because Paul had invested that time into Timothy, he knew the fine qualities that

00:07:09.420 --> 00:07:11.180
young man had.

00:07:11.180 --> 00:07:18.259
Well, Paul not only wanted Timothy to take that training himself, but you'll recall that

00:07:18.259 --> 00:07:25.939
in 2 Timothy chapter 2, he gave advice to Timothy as to what he was to do with all of that

00:07:25.939 --> 00:07:28.819
fine training that he had received.

00:07:28.819 --> 00:07:36.459
Timothy chapter 2 and verse 2, Paul said, and the things you heard from me that were

00:07:36.459 --> 00:07:45.860
supported by many witnesses, these things in trust to faithful men who in turn will be

00:07:45.860 --> 00:07:49.699
adequately qualified to teach others.

00:07:49.699 --> 00:07:57.939
